    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p>Like other adjectives, <g>fuar</g> can be used (uninflected) as the predicate of the
                verb <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with a human subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha iad <m>fuar</m> ag obair anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>They are cold working in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum fliuch agus <m>fuar</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm are wet and cold.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7 [226]</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha mi <m>fuar</m> agus tha mi sgìth.</gd>
                        <tr>I am cold and I am tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with an inanimate subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha seo <m>fuar</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>This is cold.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 15</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with an abstract subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an latha <m>fuar</m>?</gd>
                        <tr>Is the day cold?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with a non-referential subject pronoun – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha e <m>fuar</m> an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>It is cold today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Chan eil e <m>fuar</m> an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>It is not cold today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 11</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
